Lyndon R. Rive: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 10:03 AM ET
Semiconductors and Semiconductor Equipment

Company Overview of SolarCity Corporation



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Lyndon R. Rive  Co-Founder and Chief Executive Officer, SolarCity CorporationAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships40$77,318,016As of Fiscal Year 2015
Background

		Mr. Lyndon R. Rive Co-Founded SolarCity Corporation in 2006 and has been its Chief Executive Officer since July 2006. Mr. Rive founded Everdream Corporation in June 1998 and served as its Vice President. Previously, he served as Vice President of Sales at Everdream Corporation. He served as a Director of SolarCity Corporation from July 2006 to November 21, 2016. He serves as Director at Off-Grid Electric Tanzania Limited. He served as a Director of Everdream Corporation. ... Mr. Rive is a self-taught business entrepreneur, featured industry speaker and technology visionary and has been featured in Business 2.0, INC. Magazine, VARBusiness, Entrepreneurs! and Smart Reseller publications. Prior to Everdream, he founded LRS, a health product production and distribution company. As one of the most accomplished Underwater Hockey players, Mr. Rive frequently plays on the USA team in world tournaments.Read Full Background




